{"type":"article_comment","id":158225,"parentType":"article","parentId":10744,"uid":15274,"contents":"<center>《闻官军收河南河北》</center><br>\n<br>\n<center>剑外忽传收蓟北，初闻涕泪满衣裳。</center><br>\n<br>\n<center>却看妻子愁何在，漫卷诗书喜欲狂。</center><br>\n<br>\n<center>白日放歌须纵酒，青春作伴好还乡。</center><br>\n<br>\n<center>即从巴峡穿巫峡，便下襄阳向洛阳。</center>","date":"2019-12-10","agreeCount":30,"discussionCount":0}